I appreciate your help.<div><br></div><div>Indeed, it&#39;s better to create my own mechanism as mentioned Lloyd. Actually my application is a framework to stream processing (something like IBM System-S), in which I use Open MPI as communication layer and part of process management. One of this framework&#39;s features is to provide a dynamic load balance mechanism. In some situations I need to move processes between machines or temporally suspend their execution. To achieve this, I need a checkpoint/restart mechanism. It is the reason of my question.<br clear="all">
